  {
    id: "basic",
    name: "Basic",
    price: { monthly: 0, yearly: 0 },
    // ...
  },
  {
    id: "premium",
    name: "Premium",
    price: { monthly: 9.99, yearly: 99.99 },
    // ...
  },
  {
    id: "ultimate",
    name: "Ultimate",
    price: { monthly: 19.99, yearly: 199.99 },
    // ...
  },
];
```

**Replace With:**
```typescript
